{"id":232595032,"title":"熱可可亞（減糖無油含奶）","content":"📌材料📌\n\n📍可可粉（此處採用H牌無糖，至少放6 g）\n📍牛奶240 ml（ex.六甲/乳香世家/瑞穗/光泉）\n📍奶泡器（IKEA一支 $35）\n📍鋼杯或其他可以直接加熱的杯子\n\n📌可有可無的材料📌\n\n📍糖粉或黑糖粉（用有糖可可粉可以省略）\n📍小篩網\n📍糖漿或蜂蜜（依個人喜好）\n📍其他（杯底：香草/薑汁/辣椒粉/咖啡粉/鮮奶油\n最後裝飾：奶酒/橙皮/堅果粉/水果切片）\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZz.jpg\n\n\n📌做法📌\n👉可可粉與少許糖漿加入杯中\n👉倒入一半的冰牛奶\n👉手拌幾下（避免可可粉飛出）\n👉機器攪拌至顏色均勻\n👉以最小火加熱 同時以機器攪拌\nps由表層打到底層 避免大氣泡產生 奶泡較為細緻\n👉目測8分滿的時候 再倒入剩下的牛奶攪拌加熱\nps這次奶泡機抽出時 不會沾附太多泡沫\nps洗完器材 你的杯子要可以直接用手拿取 不要過熱\n👉篩上糖粉 & 可可粉\nps放在水槽過篩 方便清理\n\n\n\n📍暖到你心底的現打可可亞就完成囉~","excerpt":"材料，可可粉（此處採用H牌無糖，至少放6 g），牛奶240 ml（ex.六甲/乳香世家/瑞穗/光泉），奶泡器（IKEA一支 $35），鋼杯或其他可以直接加熱的杯子，可有可無的材料，糖粉或黑糖粉（用有糖","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:54:06.555Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-29T10:54:06.555Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":37,"tags":[],"topics":["烹飪","食譜","可可","巧克力","在家輕鬆做"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"國立臺灣海洋大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":37}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZz.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"182bfdc7-27ea-4f54-bfc5-203fe989207e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZzl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZzl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZzl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:54:06.555Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-29T10:54:06.555Z"},{"id":"182bfdc7-27ea-4f54-bfc5-203fe989207e","url":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZz.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/F9SPqZz","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/F9SPqZzl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:54:06.555Z","u